  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-119fve5\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"MfTNVl6h\">这个不应该算刻板印象，应该是性别角色认同和性别化。</p><p data-pid=\"LUcp01Ds\">在<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=41702021&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=2&amp;q=%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2%E8%AE%A4%E5%90%8C&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">性别角色认同<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>中习惯把男性视作工具性角色，女性视作支持性角色。</p><p data-pid=\"y-xBjS44\">男孩样女孩样的说法很民科，心理<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=41702021&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%8F%8C%E6%80%A7%E5%8C%96&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">双性化<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>是一种理论观点，有30%双性化，33为男性化男人和女性化女人，其余为未分化或性别倒置</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
